  "2393890": {
    "name": "伊格尼之石",
    "steam_appid": 2393890,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/e65e5e11fc5f51343d23769d7eb94d0d.avif?t=1716563952\" width=616 height=224 /></span><br><br>《IGNISTONE》是一款以精准防御为中心的Roguelike动作游戏。<br>操作虽然简单易上手，可一旦失败就会失去装备的那种“Roguelike游戏”独有的紧张感使人无法松懈。<br><br>“HP30%以下时攻击力提升3倍”“攻破敌人时HP恢复10%”等<br>可结合玩家自身游玩风格进行装备，种类繁多的护身符和武器。<br>考验玩家判断力的道具使用和路线选择等迷宫设计。<br>拓展丰富游戏世界的个性十足的角色和小游戏。<br><br><br>快来尽情体验这个IGNISTONE的世界吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/83fd0a706cc9c2c5bc548fe1cd9ca16c.avif?t=1716563952\" width=616 height=72 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/f75cc836e043934b00a54de541d94836.poster.avif?t=1716563952\" width=616 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/f75cc836e043934b00a54de541d94836.webm?t=1716563952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/f75cc836e043934b00a54de541d94836.mp4?t=1716563952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >冒险大本营</h2>豆子一族的村庄是IGNISTONE冒险的大本营。<br>与个性十足的豆子一族相识相知同时，制作自己的专属装备吧！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/47a37f6cdfedd475246a5ffc30a0f2df.webp?t=1716563952\" width=616 height=32 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/6e166f039dd630f58d4149ecd56bc8b4.poster.avif?t=1716563952\" width=616 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/6e166f039dd630f58d4149ecd56bc8b4.webm?t=1716563952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/6e166f039dd630f58d4149ecd56bc8b4.mp4?t=1716563952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >以精准防御为中心的战斗</h2>IGNISTONE的战斗动作只有“攻击”“防御”“必杀技”三种。<br>操作虽然简单，可Roguelike游戏独有的紧张感使人无法松懈。<br>看准敌人的动作，利用精准防御击败对方吧！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/47a37f6cdfedd475246a5ffc30a0f2df.webp?t=1716563952\" width=616 height=32 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/68b790422ef77c03087d6ab25b37a099.poster.avif?t=1716563952\" width=616 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/68b790422ef77c03087d6ab25b37a099.webm?t=1716563952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/68b790422ef77c03087d6ab25b37a099.mp4?t=1716563952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >变化多端的迷宫</h2>迷宫探索也是IGNISTONE的乐趣之一。<br>玩家可以从3条路线中选择其一并前进。<br>或许还会遇到专为Roguelike高级玩家而设的高难度迷宫？<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/47a37f6cdfedd475246a5ffc30a0f2df.webp?t=1716563952\" width=616 height=32 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/2d7600aaf272280f7b2d6c413120c497.poster.avif?t=1716563952\" width=616 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/2d7600aaf272280f7b2d6c413120c497.webm?t=1716563952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/2d7600aaf272280f7b2d6c413120c497.mp4?t=1716563952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >武器和护身符</h2>IGNISTONE中有各式各样的护身符和武器。<br>玩家可装备一把剑和一面盾牌，而护身符最多可佩戴8个。<br>从种类丰富的装备中，搭配自己的专属组合吧！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/47a37f6cdfedd475246a5ffc30a0f2df.webp?t=1716563952\" width=616 height=32 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/45f31d6e1a316fff5149e93be4aeebc4.poster.avif?t=1716563952\" width=626 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/45f31d6e1a316fff5149e93be4aeebc4.webm?t=1716563952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/45f31d6e1a316fff5149e93be4aeebc4.mp4?t=1716563952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >其乐无穷的世界</h2>在冒险途中，游玩小游戏稍作休息。<br>充分享受其乐无穷的豆子一族世界吧！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/6c3fbbac985a7221a3e3bb8541683f9d.avif?t=1716563952\" width=616 height=135 /></span>",
